cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper presents a parser for LFG-annotated sentences, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of statistical models and machine learning techniques, which are common in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the performance of the parser on different corpora, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of frequency estimators, which can be relevant to the sub-field of cybernetics (cs.CY).
